name: .21 SLUG LOVE FEST. Lucky Lucy van Delft
description:
an astonishing moment which had to be documented on the blockchain for all eternity...
a poly-amorous slug lovefest of epic proportions. so many questions, such as:
1. aren't these baby slugs?
2. do they even reproduce yet?
3. why are their weird translucent penises by their head?
4. wtf is that one seriously eating the residual love slime in a clean-up session after?

but if you need any kind of entertainment for while you sit outside and smoke spliffs, highly recommend some slugs and a flashlight. they are very loving to each other in ways you could never imagine. naughty naughty slugs.
